game.name: Super Onion Boy
game.description:
A bad guy has kidnapped your lover cute princess! She has been imprisoned in a magic bubble. Now you do not have any option rather than fighting against the horde of monsters to bring your love home safely. Common boys! It is a long journey, do not take it easy. There are plenty of deadly souls to deal with along the way. Can you handle them on your own? Join Super Onion Boy and be prepared to save your beautiful princess by completing multiple levels!

This brand-new adventure challenge has a resemblance to a popular platformer game inspired by the Mario series. When your character runs, make sure to keep him away from all his enemies. Try to beat or avoid them to get him going in this HTML54 platform game! Do not forget to grab as much props and coins as you can to save your life. Remember you would have only limited lives 5 to lose in each level. Complete your task before the time runs out in this cool runner challenge!

Catch all the superpowers to make your character powerful with firepower, super leap and invincibility! You can also grab the coins and hidden lives and stars to earn the extra lives. We are pretty confident that you will guide this cute character through all 15 unique and challenging levels. Score high in each level to top the leaderboard and do not forget to share your final score with your friends and family! Check out and play many popular free platformer games on atmegame.com for free!
